359
00:22:08,160 --> 00:22:11,920
<i>I'll let Li Mian show you
how he gets along with women.</i>

360
00:22:14,079 --> 00:22:15,640
<i>That's great.</i>

361
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:17,680
