377
00:22:55,400 --> 00:22:56,599
Learn from him quickly.

378
00:22:58,239 --> 00:23:00,160
<i>I can't let him learn from Li Mian.</i>

379
00:23:03,680 --> 00:23:05,560
You are handsome,

380
00:23:05,560 --> 00:23:08,920
