417
00:25:12,439 --> 00:25:16,040
<i>He didn't realize that Zhou Yuan was a woman.</i>

418
00:25:16,680 --> 00:25:17,940
<i>I'm not jealous.</i>

419
00:25:17,940 --> 00:25:19,280
