425
00:25:31,439 --> 00:25:34,340
<i>Should I tell him the truth? Forget it.</i>

426
00:25:34,340 --> 00:25:36,199
<i>It seems more fun not to tell him.</i>

427
00:25:37,560 --> 00:25:39,040
