484
00:28:24,119 --> 00:28:25,319
And I don't care how you use it.

485
00:28:28,119 --> 00:28:29,888
It's all up to you.

486
00:28:29,888 --> 00:28:31,079
Good.

487
00:28:33,120 --> 00:28:34,280
Wait.

488
00:28:35,239 --> 00:28:37,340
